 🖥️ Cybersecurity Workstation PC Build

 📌 Overview
This project documents the end-to-end process of building and configuring a custom desktop PC designed for cybersecurity tasks such as virtualization, ethical hacking, and digital forensics.

The goal was to create a **high-performance and stable environment** capable of running multiple virtual machines while maintaining strong system performance and reliability.

